name: Roy Tang
text: While this video is nice, it doesn't really answer the question in the title because it doesn't provide any comparison to our neighbors so that we know which components are overpriced! Even if we have the rate adjustments due to guaranteed 15% profits, our costs should be at most 15% higher than our neighbors on average, not the 900% shown in the video.
